      <description>Multi level marketing companies&amp;#8216; concepts are too darn simple – you build a network of people and jointly you promote a product or service. At the same time you try to bring more people into the network. For each person that joins the network the upline members earn a commission. Direct sales bring in the [...]&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/experience-seekers-travel-club/Experience_Seekers_Travel_Club-Multi_Level_Marketing_Companies-_Generating_A_Healthy_Business_Of_Your_Own.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://www.selflearningclub.com/info/isagenix.htm">Multi level marketing companies</a>&#8216; concepts are too darn simple – you build a network of people and jointly you promote a product or service. At the same time you try to bring more people into the network. For each person that joins the network the upline members earn a commission. Direct sales bring in the money too, but the main income is brought in through the commissions that the network building generates.</p>
<p>Building the network can be formidable for some people. Even so, there are plenty of sources of help so that you can build a solid network. You receive a website from the network marketing company that you join, you can attend physical seminars and webinars and you have access to a host of material, online and offline, where you can learn how to promote your network to the hilt.</p>
<p>You need to remember one thing – joining the <a href="http://www.selflearningclub.com/info/isagenix">multi level marketing companies</a>&#8216; opportunity could be a life-changing experience. You might begin seeing everything in a totally new light. But that’s also the way you can earn that six figure income.</p>
<p>The most popular <strong>multi level marketing companies</strong> around the world promote themselves on a global level. Joining carries the great benefit of prevailing goodwill that you can use to build your business. Also, these companies have their own training and orientation programs which you can access no matter where you live which can help you start out on the right foot.</p>
<p>Robert Kiyosaki, best known for his series of books &#8220;Rich Dad, Poor Dad&#8221; is a proponent of multi level marketing companies and said &#8220;Why not build a network marketing business in your spare time? Why not build something you control and you own?&#8221; &#8220;The reason I recommend network marketing is because network marketing is the business of the future&#8221;.</p>
<p>He also says the two essential reasons to join a network marketing business is, one to help yourself and two, to help others. If you join for only one of these two reasons, then the system will not work for you.</p>
<p>One company that epitomises the help others and help yourself philosophy is Isagenix. Isagenix is part of the health and wellness industry and manufactures and markets products for nutritional cleansing.</p>
<p>Isagenix is a company that embraces the help others/help yourself philosophy. Everyone starts out as a consumer of the products and because of the wonderful benefits gained from using the product people then move on to begin their own business. They have the results from using the Isagenix nutritional cleanse products to show others(reason 1),who in turn become advocates and show others the benefits gained and so on. Meanwhile you are healthy and on your way to wealthy as your <em>multilevel network marketing</em> business is growing(reason 2). </p>
<p>The Isagenix <strong>multi level network marketing</strong> business opportunity suits most people looking to start their own business &#8211; either as an add on income stream to an established business or as something for the person looking to escape the 9-5 and operate a business from home. </p>
]]></content:encoded>
